u2013 One Direction \u2013 What Makes You Beautiful|id=User must enter \"One Direction\" in the search bar and click \"S\u00f8k\"|publisher=[[IFPI]] Norway}}</ref>|type=single|award=Platinum|number=7}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Sweden|relyear=2011|certyear=2012|title=What Makes You Beautiful|artist=One Direction|type=single|award=Platinum|number=4}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Switzerland|relyear=2011|certyear=2013|title=What Makes You Beautiful|artist=One Direction|type=single|award=Platinum}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|relyear=2011|certyear=2013|title=What Makes You Beautiful|artist=One Direction|type=single|award=Platinum|number=3|salesamount=1,000,000|salesref=<ref name=\"UK sales\">{{cite news|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/one-directions-what-makes-you-beautiful-is-the-uks-latest-million-selling-song__16568/|title=One Direction's What Makes You Beautiful is the UK's latest million-selling song|last=Myers|first=Justin|date=8 October 2016|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|access-date=8 October 2016}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|relyear=2011|certyear=2012|title=What Makes You Beautiful|artist=One Direction|type=single|award=Platinum|number=4|salesamount=4,888,000|salesref=<ref name=\"USsales2016\"/>}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}\n\n==Release history==\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"| Region\n!scope=\"col\"| Date\n!scope=\"col\"| Format\n!scope=\"col\"| Label\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Australia<ref name=\"AUSiTunes\">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/what-makes-you-beautiful/id452514272|title=What Makes You Beautiful|publisher=[[iTunes Store]] ([[Apple Inc.]]) |accessdate=3 January 2012}}</ref>\n|rowspan=\"18\"| 11 September 2011\n|rowspan=\"18\"| [[Music download|Digital download]]\n|rowspan=\"22\"| [[Syco Music]]\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Belgium<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/be/album/what-makes-you-beautiful/id452514272|title